➜宁夏银川：禁止中小学生将手机、平板电脑等电子产品带入校园
http://www.sohu.com/a/413883756_162758	26763
<p>宁夏银川：禁止中小学生将手机、平板电脑等电子产品带入校园</p>
<p>新华社银川8月19日电（记者艾福梅）记者从宁夏回族自治区银川市教育局获悉，自今年秋季开学起，全市中小学校、幼儿园将全面禁止学生携带智能手机、平板电脑等电子产品进校园。</p>
<p>根据银川市教育局下发的通知，学校因教育教学工作需要学生使用平板电脑的，应指定专人加强管理，严禁学生使用平板电脑进行与教育教学无关的活动。凡违规带入校园的，学校应指定专人统一保管或通知学生家长领回。</p>
<p>针对部分家长与学生需要联系的情况，银川市要求各学校结合实际、免费为学生提供与家长联系的固定电话等通信工具，并向家长公布学校有关办公室、班主任和管理人员等的联系方式，方便家长沟通学情、联系学生。</p>
➜Sputnik: China economy sets an example casting off the impact of the pandemic, Russian expert said
http://www.sohu.com/a/413884592_162758	27118
<p align="center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200819/576605334463496a883bf70bdb4dc4fd.png" /></p>
<p align="justify">Sputnik reported on Aug 14 that Russian experts spoke at an online conference reviewing the global oil market that China had shown the world how it effectively got rid of the economic impact of the novel coronavirus pandemic.</p>
<p align="justify">Dr. Vyacheslav Kulagin, the director of the Institute for Economics and Regulation of Natural Monopolies at HSE University and the director of Scientific Research of the Energy Research Institute of Russian Academy of Sciences (RAS), stressed during an online meeting that China has now set an example how it shrugged off the impact caused by the COVID-19 pandemic.</p>
<p align="justify">Experts pointed out that China’s experience fighting against the pandemic has been fairly meaningful. “China has made precise measures to prevent the spread of the coronavirus in the country, acting immediately after discovering the source of infection and taking strict quarantine measures. Firstly get the problems solved, and then lift the restrictions.”</p>
<p align="justify">Dr. Kulagin believed that China has shown the world how it managed to regulate to avoid economic difficulties and effectively get rid of the impact. He also deemed that China plays an important role in stabilizing the price of the oil market.</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p align="justify">As decisive steps have already been taken in China’s fight against the pandemic, it may be safe to say now that the country’s economy can be lifted from the impact without huge losses. China’s demand for energy resource will soon be restored, which can be a positive effect on the world oil market, as the oil price has dropped to a record low in spring, reaching US$20 per barrel or even lower. China has built up necessary storage capacity and has seized the chance to buy in large quantities of oil at the low price. In May, the country’s oil imports exceeded the record (11.34 million barrels per day). Procurement by Chinese companies has become the main reason for the rise in oil prices.</p>
<p align="justify">Alexey Gromov, the principal director on Energy Studies, Institute for Energy and Finance in Russia, indicated that China is extremely important to the world oil market in the second quarter of 2020 as it has the outbreak under control.</p>
<p align="justify">In his words, “China’s recovery of energy demand has a strong impact on the world market. Unlike other countries that just started to take quarantine measures in the second quarter, China has already started the active purchase of energy resource.”</p>
<p align="justify">Find out more of the original article at http://sputniknews.cn/economics/202008151031968951/</p>
<p>[责任编辑: WXY ] </p>
➜美疾控中心：全美近1.7万名孕妇感染新冠病毒
http://www.sohu.com/a/413884769_162758	27124
<p>【美疾控中心：全美近1.7万名孕妇感染新冠病毒】美国疾病控制与预防中心（CDC）日前表示，全美目前已有近1.7万名孕妇感染新冠病毒，其中37人死亡。据福克斯5频道18日报道，美国疾控中心的最新数据显示，从1月22日至8月11日，全美共有16798名孕妇的新冠肺炎检测结果呈阳性，其中近一半的患者为拉丁裔。据悉，因病住院的孕妇为4262人。美国广播公司等媒体7月9日曾援引美疾控中心的数据报道，当时共有11312名孕妇被诊断出感染新冠病毒。（海外网，LS）</p>
